@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.80) + (tmp + 0.66 + v0 + 0.59)) * tmp)
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.76) * ((v1 + 0.22 + v0 + 0.21) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v1 + 0.52 - v1 + 0.25)))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = 0.36
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.47) - (v1 + 0.80 - v2 + 0.82)) + v1)
    tmp = 0.93
    data[tid] = v0
